title: Private Central London Office Space £ 600 Per Month Inclusive
body:
QR Code Link to This Post


Central London private self-contained office for rent, located near Tottenham Court Road and Holborn stations just off  New Oxford Street Approx 200 sq/ feet and can comfortably accommodate up to 3 desks. Furniture (ie cabinets, desks & chairs) provided Free superfast Virgin Media 90 mbs fibre optics broadband 
The monthly rent is £600 p/m which includes all utility bills and rates 
No minimum contractual period to tie you down so ideal for start-ups  
Please drop me a note or call to arrange a viewing 
Thanks
John
